                <head>489. Summary of Conclusions of a Special Coordination Committee Meeting<note
                        n="1" type="source" xml:id="d489fn1">Source: Carter Library, National
                        Security Council, Institutional Files, Box 93, <gloss target="#t_SCC_1"
                            >SCC</gloss> 074, <gloss target="#t_SSOD_1">SSOD</gloss>—U.S.
                        Presentation and Initiative: 5/5/78. Secret. The meeting took place in the
                        White House Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            from="1978-05-12T09:00:00-04:00" to="1978-05-12T10:00:00-04:00">May 12,
                            1978, 9:00–10:00 a.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>United Nations Special Session on Disarmament</item>
                </list>
                <list type="participants">
                    <head>PARTICIPANTS</head>
